text:
Early react from Dem presidential candidates is fairly uniform.
Warren: "Release the Mueller report now."
O'Rourke: "Release the Mueller report to the American people."
Harris: "The report must be released immediately."
Sanders: "As Donald Trump said, 'Let it come out.' "
